{"title":"FUNETHIC","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eFUN!ETHIC offers top quality beauty treasures. Their treatments are natural, certified organic and not tested on animals. Brand's cosmetics are organized by categories: “Being a Teen”, “Being 20”, “Being a Woman” and “For All”. These beauty routines are accompanied by hygiene products: handmade soaps and shower gels. Formulations are exemplary: the brand goes well beyond the specifications of cosmetics by banishing all controversial substances. FUN!ETHIC is Ecocert and Peta certified, Cosmebio label and winners of the Slow Cosmetics mention.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","products":[{"product_id":"cosmos-organic-certified-extra-gentle-shower-gel-fruity-wild-strawberry-250ml","title":"Cosmos Organic Certified Extra Gentle Shower Gel - Fruity Wild Strawberry 250ml","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eExtra gentle and certified \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eorganic natural shower gel with a delicious and fruity 100% natural wild strawberry scent. Enriched with natural glycerin, it gently cleanses and moisturizes the skin.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eIts exemplary formula is respectful of your skin and the environment: without sulfates, parabens, PEG, phenoxyethanol or cocamidopropyl betaine. Its creamy texture, delicate foam and fresh lemon verbana scent create a real moment of relaxation in your shower.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eThe shower gel is suitable for all skin types and will be appreciated by the whole family. Children under 3 years old are not recommended to use this shower gel.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e Wild strawberry shower gel can be used daily on the face and body. Apply the shower gel on the body, avoid the eye area. Rinse and dry. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Aqua (water), hordeum stem water*, lauryl glucoside, sodium cocoyl glutamate, glycerin, coco glucoside, citric acid, glyceryl oleate, parfum (fragrance), sodium benzoate, potassium sorbate.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e* Ingredient from Organic Farming\u003cbr\u003e** Processed from ingredients from Organic Farming\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eMade in France.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eIngredients 99.5% natural and 10.5% from organic farming\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eAll raw materials processed in France\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eShower gel made in France (Alsace)\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eNo controversial ingredients , 100% good for your skin\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eWithout palm oil or derivatives\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eDoes not release pollutants into water\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003ePackaging: 100% recycled and recyclable bottle made in Europe\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e","brand":"FUN!ETHIC","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49111920607559,"sku":"","price":6.5,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/cosmos-organic-certified-extra-gentle-shower-gel-fruity-wild-strawberry-250ml-376157.png?v=1739897340"},{"product_id":"cosmos-organic-certified-extra-gentle-shower-gel-discreet-saline-scent-250ml","title":"Cosmos Organic Certified Extra Gentle Shower Gel - Discreet Saline Scent 250ml","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eExtra gentle and certified \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eorganic natural shower gel with a discreet marine and saline scent. Enriched with natural glycerin, it gently cleanses and moisturizes the skin.  \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eIts exemplary formula is respectful of your skin and the environment: without sulfates, parabens, PEG, phenoxyethanol or cocamidopropyl betaine. Its creamy texture, delicate foam and fresh lemon verbana scent create a real moment of relaxation in your shower.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eThe shower gel is suitable for all skin types and will be appreciated by the whole family. Children under 3 years old are not recommended to use this shower gel.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e Marine shower gel can be used daily on the face and body. Apply the shower gel on the body, avoid the eye area. Rinse and dry.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Aqua (water), hordeum stem water*, lauryl glucoside, sodium cocoyl glutamate, glycerin, coco glucoside, citric acid, glyceryl oleate, parfum (fragrance), benzyl salicylate, geraniol, sodium benzoate, potassium sorbate.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e* Ingredient from Organic Farming\u003cbr\u003e** Processed from ingredients from Organic Farming\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eMade in France.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eIngredients 99.5% natural and 10.5% from organic farming\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eAll raw materials processed in France\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eShower gel made in France (Alsace)\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eNo controversial ingredients, 100% good for your skin\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eWithout palm oil or derivatives\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eDoes not release pollutants into water\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003ePackaging:  100% recycled and recyclable bottle made in Europe \u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e","brand":"FUN!ETHIC","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49111947116871,"sku":null,"price":6.5,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/cosmos-organic-certified-extra-gentle-shower-gel-discreet-saline-scent-250ml-846314.png?v=1739897339"},{"product_id":"cosmos-organic-certified-extra-gentle-shower-gel-refreshing-tonic-scent-250ml","title":"Cosmos Organic Certified Extra Gentle Shower Gel - Refreshing Tonic Scent 250ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eExtra gentle and certified \u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eorganic natural shower gel with an invigorating and refreshing 100% natural lemon verbena scent. Enriched with natural glycerin, it gently cleanses and moisturizes the skin.  \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eIts exemplary formula is respectful of your skin and the environment: without sulfates, parabens, PEG, phenoxyethanol or cocamidopropyl betaine. Its creamy texture, delicate foam and fresh lemon verbana scent create a real moment of relaxation in your shower. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eThe shower gel is suitable for all skin types and will be appreciated by the whole family. Children under 3 years old are not recommended to use this shower gel.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e Lemon verbena shower gel can be used daily on the face and body. Apply the shower gel on the body, avoid the eye area. Rinse and dry. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Aqua (water), hordeum stem water*, lauryl glucoside, sodium cocoyl glutamate, glycerin, coco glucoside, citric acid, glyceryl oleate, parfum (fragrance), citral, limonene, sodium benzoate, potassium sorbate.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e* Ingredient from Organic Farming\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e** Processed from ingredients from Organic Farming\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eMade in France.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eIngredients 99.5% natural and 10.5% from organic farming\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eAll raw materials processed in France\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eShower gel made in France (Alsace)\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eNo controversial ingredients, 100% good for your skin\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eWithout palm oil or derivatives\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eDoes not release pollutants into water\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003ePackaging: 100% recycled and recyclable bottles made in Europe\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e","brand":"FUN!ETHIC","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49112004165959,"sku":null,"price":6.5,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/cosmos-organic-certified-extra-gentle-shower-gel-refreshing-tonic-scent-250ml-391460.png?v=1739897343"},{"product_id":"deodorant-cosmebio-without-aluminum-salts-without-alcohol-without-parabens-50ml","title":"Deodorant Cosmébio Without Aluminum Salts Without Alcohol Without Parabens 50ml","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe natural and certified organic “Avoir 20 Ans” alcohol-free roll-on deodorant has been tested effective for 24 hours. It is also free of aluminum salts and parabens. The aloe vera contained in the treatment makes it very moisturizing, it is ideal after hair removal to avoid redness. Its antibacterial active ingredients prevent appearance of post-depilatory pimples. Its small ball allows it to be applied precisely and it does not stain clothes. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eIt is suitable for all skin types. Its creamy texture and very light 100% natural orange blossom fragrance will delight you every day.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/b\u003eThe “Avoir 20 Ans” deodorant is used in the morning and\/or evening after a shower on clean, dry skin, applying gently under the armpits. Repeat the application during the day when you feel the need.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eAqua, hordeum vulgare stem water*, caprylic\/capric triglycerides, triethyl citrate, cetearyl alcohol, glyceryl stearate, glycerin, stearic acid, prunus persica juice, aloe vera barbadensis powder*, tocopherol, helianthus annuus seed oil, salvia officinalis (sage) oil , sodium caproyl\/lauroyl lactyl lactate, sodium lauroyl glutamate, xanthan gum, citric acid, sodium benzoate, potassium sorbate, benzyl alcohol, dehydroacetic acid, fragrance, linalool, limonene, geraniol, citral.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e* Ingredient from Organic Farming\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cspan\u003e** Processed from ingredients from Organic Farming\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eMade in France.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e99.5% natural ingredients, 12.9% from organic farming and mainly from fair trade\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eAll raw materials processed in France\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eDeodorant made in France (Alsace)\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eNo controversial ingredients, 100% good for your skin and the enivironment\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eTotal absence of palm oil and its derivatives\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003ePackaging: 100% recycled and recyclable bottle made in Europe\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e","brand":"FUN!ETHIC","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49112020844871,"sku":null,"price":6.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/deodorant-cosmebio-without-aluminum-salts-without-alcohol-without-parabens-50ml-431679.png?v=1739897342"}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/collections\/funethic-330879.png?v=1739979835","url":"https:\/\/bioskina.com\/collections\/funethic.oembed","provider":"bioskina","version":"1.0","type":"link"}